Define a detailed use-case specification for the main use-case of a customer renting a car. (4 marks)

Use case name: Car Rental

Brief description: Customer rents a car based on their specifications.

Initiating Actor: Customer

Actor's goal: To rent a car

Participating actors: Company, system, managers, staff, insurance guy

Flow of events only for the Main Success usage scenario:
    1. Customer searches for a car based on criteria.
    2. Customer selects a car and books it, entering payment details.
    3. System processes the payment details and holds the information while manager records car rented.
    4. System returns a payment confirmation email to the customer.

    
